machine_start_gcode:
;ELEGOO NEPTUNE 4 PRO

M220 S100 ;Set the feed speed to 100%
M221 S100 ;Set the flow rate to 100%
M104 S270
M190 S[bed_temperature_initial_layer_single]
G90
G28 ;home
SET_PRESSURE_ADVANCE SMOOTH_TIME=0.02
;BED_MESH_CLEAR
;BED_MESH_PROFILE LOAD=12-80-FULA          ;load the best mesh we have, with 12 probe points
; calling the KAMP after doing config in printer.cfg - all paramenters are set in KAMP_settings.cfg
BED_MESH_CALIBRATE 
G1 Z10 F300
G1 X20 Y40 F6000
G1 Z0 F300
M109 S[nozzle_temperature_initial_layer]
G92 E0 ;Reset Extruder
G1 X10 Y50 Z0.4 F3000 ;Move to start position
G1 Y100 E30 F400 ;Draw the first line
G1 Z0.6 F120.0 ;Move to side a little
G1 X162.5 F3000
G92 E0 ;Reset Extruder
name: Neptune 4 Pro (0.4 nozzle) - PETG-CF  KAMP
printer_notes: 245 is too hot for PETG, use 240 max, likely best at 235
